# Re-include pre-built standalone output for the Dockerfile.prebuilt deploy
# path (assembles the runner image from artifacts built off-box or in a
# resource-limited container, bypassing an in-image `next build`). Harmless
# to the regular Dockerfile, which builds its own .next inside the image.
